{"tid":2243803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「台灣No.1」淘寶台灣被收皮","createTime":"2020-10-15T04:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T10:25:13.000Z","uid":20815,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3dce8c4094a84a44f5ba7cd371400799bee541e4","tid":2243803,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/157439?fbclid=IwAR0dElVuxKc2mk5m2GsMP4N5udHjkZ_-WSmNOrCflMrKhDFHwxZ0lMkP4Es\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F157439%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dElVuxKc2mk5m2GsMP4N5udHjkZ_-WSmNOrCflMrKhDFHwxZ0lMkP4Es&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=6a904873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/157439?fbclid=IwAR0dElVuxKc2mk5m2GsMP4N5udHjkZ_-WSmNOrCflMrKhDFHwxZ0lMkP4Es</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先前因中資投資相關問題，遭經濟部投審會要求限期改善的淘寶台灣，根據財經新報等媒體報導今天其營運公司英商克雷達宣布，將在2020年底停止台灣相關營運服務，淘寶台灣從現在起關閉平台下單、商品上架、賣家入駐等功能。但既有的交易訂單將盡速履行，台灣員工將妥善規劃給予相關保障權益，並與人力銀行合作協助轉介。<br />\n<br />\n英商克雷達先前獲得阿里巴巴集團授權其淘寶品牌後，在台灣推出電商平台淘寶台灣，開站不到1年時間就引發資金爭議。8月時，經濟部投資審議委會員調查後發現，阿里巴巴對克雷達有實際掌控能力，且未依照中資來台投資申請相關許可，要求其撤回投資或改正。10月15日英商克雷達發出聲明，表示將在2020年底停止台灣相關營運服務，即日起關閉下單等功能，既有訂單將協助履行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想偷雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73515df21e67ccf85701bba535727e1f9baf269c","tid":2243803,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"用開XX來買飛雞杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982a4b69d11e6579b929042dcf43d3a9c88fac79","tid":2243803,"uid":278524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"口交部：拿石頭砸自己的腳"},{"pid":"b0ce82402d79f0e7b33a21ea544ab2e7e95747ed","tid":2243803,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"用英國公司 想側側膊唔多覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a452be7e0998d067be482a07075fcdb974f14708","tid":2243803,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650e4b9a813c3addae7cbbf4b4d4dfdf0a314bf3","tid":2243803,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"03c498642d747b6c2a1c9dfaad2de9ef7061c840","tid":2243803,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"台灣大把地方取代到淘寶啦"},{"pid":"154ef6ba10d789833024ab6b9af6ae6c133c8fae","tid":2243803,"uid":38434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a779e03d68fed674448f464fc3924e1d77b1352","tid":2243803,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係興蝦皮咩"},{"pid":"a2ab72184dfbc3134e7df5d6f7428e2b92e64545","tid":2243803,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"蝦皮咪又係賣淘寶貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a0d9000715bfafb7cf8744c0b8a659a8947b3","tid":2243803,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"冇得淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係唔移民台灣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b3d93fd9a88f6ef9838d2c2fc20e8c5e7bdfa4","tid":2243803,"uid":199496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"淘寶支持台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ea5f6c71a92445f953daee3b5fd778fd5608d9","tid":2243803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco